data.description: This condo community only accepts cash or Conventional financing.  This attractive unit features 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, hardwood floors throughout, an eat-in kitchen with a stacked washer and dryer, stainless steel appliances, and a living room with a sunroom. It includes 1 reserved parking space and 2 additional parking permits. The community, conveniently near Glenmont Metro with bus transportation, offers 2 outdoor pools and a community center. Condo fees cover water. Close access to ICC 200 and major commuter routes, Layhill shopping center where most of your necessities can be found, Northwest golf course, and many trails and parks.
